This directory contains essential setup and configuration files to get coverage through Catapult Coverage (CCOV) and Catapult Formal CoverCheck (CCoverCheck):

 ---------------------------------------
Created and Verified with the following tool versions:
   Catapult      2025.2
   CCOV          2025.1
   QuestaSim     2025.1
   CoverCheck    2025.1
 ---------------------------------------

Steps:

1. Set the required environment variables:

    setenv CCOV_HOME /path to CCOV install
    setenv QUESTA_HOME /Path to Questa Install
    setenv CATAPULT_HOME /path to Mgc_home
    setenv SLEC_HOME /path to SLEC Install or $CATAPULT_HOME/pkgs/cds_cpc/rls

2. Run CDesignChecker and Generate .design_checker_db through Catapult:

    make cat_cdc  (default ARGS=SINGLE_PROCESS)
    make cat_cdc ARGS=MULTI_PROCESS
    make cat_cdc ARGS=BANKED_MULTI_PROCESS

3. Compile and Instrument design with CCOV, generate the initial UCDB file from the CCOV generated data:

    make run_ccov  (default ARGS=SINGLE_PROCESS)
    make run_ccov ARGS=MULTI_PROCESS
    make run_ccov ARGS=BANKED_MULTI_PROCESS

4. Run CCoverCheck and Apply CCoverCheck-generated exclusions to the initial UCDB using Visualizer:

    make run_ccovercheck

%> In order to Perform Steps 2 to 4:
    
    make all  (default ARGS=SINGLE_PROCESS)
    make all ARGS=MULTI_PROCESS
    make all ARGS=BANKED_MULTI_PROCESS

5. View UCDB file in Visualizer after applying CCoverCheck-generated exclusions:

    make ccovercheck_viewcov

6. If desired, delete generated files:

    make clean
 
%> To get the information about the all targets and environment variables:

    make help
